      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp six-speed manual transmission. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by a variable M differential lock and a weight-optimized suspension utilizing aluminum components. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the 8,400 RPM redline can be enjoyed with peace of mind. The hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback lost in modern EPS systems. While the exterior shows honest signs of spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain rigidity remain tight, making this an ideal candidate for the purist who values visceral performance and engineering integrity.",
